Ejercicio 1 — Media
Ingresa la media (2–3 decimales):
&lt;input id="ans_media" type="number" step="0.01" style="width:140px;"&gt;&lt;button onclick="(function(){const v=parseFloat(document.getElementById('ans_media').value);const sol=Number(r round(media_real,6));const ok=Math.abs(v-sol)&lt;=Math.max(0.01,Math.abs(sol)*0.002);document.getElementById('out_media').textContent= ok ? "✅ Correcto" : ❌ Incorrecto. La media era ${sol.toFixed(2)};})()"&gt;Verificar&lt;/button&gt;
&lt;div id="out_media" style="margin-top:6px;"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
